              },
              "bullet_points": "• Includes a Stephanie mini-doll figure, plus a Dash puppy figure.\r\n• Features a soccer goal with moving goalkeeper platform, soccer ball launcher with shooting function, strategy board and a drinks station.\r\n• Accessory elements include a ball, water bottle, hot dog, dog bowl and a bone.\r\n• Brush up on tactics at the strategy board, and practice your aim by shooting the ball at the goal.\r\n• Ask a friend to control the goalkeeper and then swap roles to see who scores the most with this great children’s toy.\r\n• Help puppy Dash run to fetch the ball and give him a bone as a treat.\r\n• Soccer goal measures over 3” (10cm) high, 3” (9cm) wide and 3” (9cm) deep.\r\n• Soccer ball launcher measures over 1” (4cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 1” (4cm) deep.\r\n• Strategy board measures over 1” (4cm) high, 1” (3cm) wide and under 1” (1cm) deep.\r\n• Combine with 41332 Emma's Art Stand, 41333 Olivia's Mission Vehicle, 41334 Andrea's Park Performance and 41335 Mia's Tree House for more fun in Heartlake City Park.",
              "comm_bullet_points": "• Build this LEGO Friends set featuring a goal net with moving goalkeeper platform, soccer ball launcher with shooting function, strategy board and a drinks station!\r\n• This sportspark building set includes a LEGO Friends Stephanie mini-doll figure, plus a Dash the pet dog figure\r\n• Soccer goal measures over 3” (10cm) high, 3” (9cm) wide and 3” (9cm) deep;Soccer ball launcher measures over 1” (4cm) high, 2” (6cm) wide and 1” (4cm) deep;Strategy board measures over 1” (4cm) high, 1” (3cm) wide and under 1” (1cm) deep\r\n• 119 pieces – Sports toy for boys and girls between the ages of 6 and 12 years\r\n• LEGO Friends building toys are compatible with all LEGO construction sets for creative building",
              "display_title": "Stephanie's Soccer Practice",
              "one_liner": "Practice penalty shoot-outs all day with Stephanie’s Soccer Practice, including a goal with moving goalkeeper platform, ball-shooting function and a strategy board.",
              "description": "Keep in training with LEGO® Friends 41330 Stephanie’s Soccer Practice in Heartlake City Park, and you’ll soon have the best aim in all of Heartlake! Use the shoot function to launch the ball toward the goal and then move Stephanie’s platform from side to side to help her make an acrobatic save. You can play on your own or with a friend! Help puppy Dash fetch the ball, then take a break with a drink and hot dog while checking out the strategy board.",
              "title": "Stephanie's Soccer Practice",
              "headline": "Score goal after goal with Stephanie and Dash!",
